						<div class="postbody">In a logarithmic pitch environment like MIDI, when you bend up or down farther than a couple semitones, you probably want to do it with a legato noteon so that the base note for the bend gets rewritten. General MIDI, for instance, appears to have a range of +/- 2 semitones for the pitch bend command.</div>

